---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { DEFAULT_EDITION } from '../lib/editions';
---
<BaseLayout
  edition={DEFAULT_EDITION}
  pathOverride="/medical-disclaimer/"
  title="Medical Disclaimer"
  description="TheWellnessGPT is educational and is not a substitute for professional medical advice. See a doctor or pharmacist before starting supplements or for persistent symptoms."
>
  <article class="article">
    <div class="wrap">
      <h1>Medical disclaimer</h1>
      <div class="article-body">
        <p>TheWellnessGPT publishes educational information about wellness, nutrition, and supplements. It is written carefully and sourced responsibly, but it is general information, not personal medical advice.</p>

        <h2>This is not a substitute for a professional</h2>
        <p>Nothing on this site is a diagnosis or a treatment plan for your specific situation. Everyone's health, history, and medication are different. If you are unsure about a symptom or a supplement, a doctor or pharmacist can assess you properly.</p>

        <h2>When to see a doctor</h2>
        <p>Please seek professional care if a symptom is severe, persistent, or getting worse; if you are pregnant or breastfeeding; if you manage a chronic condition (such as diabetes, or kidney, liver, or heart disease); if you take prescription medication; or before you stop, start, or combine treatments. Supplements can interact with medication and with each other.</p>

        <h2>Supplements are not regulated like medicine</h2>
        <p>Supplement quality, dose, and purity vary between brands and between countries, and "supports" or "helps" on a label is not the same as "treats" or "cures." More is not better; some nutrients are harmful in excess. We try to flag effective doses and known risks, but always follow the product label and professional guidance.</p>

        <h2>Individual results vary</h2>
        <p>Ingredients and products affect people differently. Introduce one new thing at a time, give it a fair trial, and stop using anything that causes a persistent or adverse reaction. If a reaction is severe, seek medical help immediately.</p>

        <p>By using this site you understand that TheWellnessGPT and its editors are not responsible for decisions made based on this general information. When in doubt, talk to a professional.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
